| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3692 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f9767a5-0903-5db1-a0b2-f8af8438b478"
